Tumor Context
</a> by Hua-Sheng Chiu, Sonal Somvanshi, et al.</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ccell.2018.07.001" class="" target="_none">Comprehensive Analysis of Alternative Splicing Across Tumors from 8,705 Patients</a> by André Kahles, Kjong-Van Lehmann, et al.</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.celrep.2018.03.047" class="" target="_none">Integrated Genomic Analysis of the Ubiquitin Pathway across Cancer Types</a> by Zhongqi Ge, Jake S. Leighton, et al.</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ccell.2018.03.007" class="" target="_none">Genomic and Functional Approaches to Understanding Cancer Aneuploidy</a> by Alison M. Taylor, Juliann Shih, et al.</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://cgc-accounts.sbgenomics.com/" class="" target="_none">Cancer Genomics Cloud</a> by <a href="https://docs.sevenbridges.com/docs/tcga-data" target="_none">Seven Bridges</a></li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
