          <p>The Real-time Analysis and Discovery in Integrated And Networked Technologies (RADIANT) initiative seeks to develop an extensible, federated framework for rapid exchange of  multimodal clinical and research data on behalf of accelerated discovery and patient impact. Coordination and implementation of initial RADIANT deployments will leverage a network of  more than 35 partnered health care systems and participating patient families within the  Children’s Brain Tumor Network (CBTN) and the Pediatric Neuro-Oncology Consortium (PNOC).  This data set is composed of public multi-modal data provisio...</p>
