          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://ard.maxar.com/docs/sdk/sdk/data-access/" class="" target="_none">Data Access (SDK tutorial)</a> by <a href="https://www.maxar.com/open-data" target="_none">Maxar Open Data</a></li></a>
          </li>
