            <a href="https://github.com/giswqs/maxar-open-data/" class="" target="_none">Visualizing Turkey &amp; Syria Earthquake Maxar Open Data with SageMaker Studio Lab</a> by <a href="https://geography.utk.edu/about-us/faculty/dr-qiusheng-wu/" target="_none">Qiusheng Wu</a></li></a>
