          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://tidesandcurrents.noaa.gov/ofs/publications/NOS-TIN-TBOFS.pdf" class="" target="_none">Technical Implementation Notice for Tampa Bay OFS</a> by NOAA</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://opendap.co-ops.nos.noaa.gov/ofsdataagg/index.html" class="" target="_none">OFS Data Aggregation and Sub-Setting</a> by NOAA</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://tidesandcurrents.noaa.gov/ofs/publications/TBOFS_Onepager.pdf" class="" target="_none">Tampa Bay OFS Flyer</a> by NOAA</li></a>
          </li>
