        </div>
        <div id="opentargets" class="dataset">
          <h3><a href="/opentargets/">Open Targets</a></h3>
          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">bioinformatics</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">biology</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">drug discovery</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">genetic</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">genomic</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">life sciences</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">protein</span></p>
          <p>The Open Targets Platform is a comprehensive data integration tool that supports systematic identification and prioritisation of potential therapeutic drug targets. By integrating publicly available datasets including data generated by the Open Targets experimental and informatics research programmes, the Platform provides data and services to assist in the task of therapeutic hypothesis building.</p>
          <p><a href="/opentargets/">Details &rarr;</a></p>
