          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://platform.opentargets.org/" class="" target="_none">Open Targets Platform Web Application</a> by <a href="https://github.com/opentargets/ot-ui-apps" target="_none">Open Targets</a></li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.ebi.ac.uk/training/online/courses/open-targets-quick-tour/" class="" target="_none">Open Targets informatics tools</a> by <a href="https://www.ebi.ac.uk/people/person/helena-cornu/" target="_none">Helena Cornu</a></li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/opentargets/notebooks" class="" target="_none">ChEMBL Evidence Data Download</a> by <a href="https://github.com/opentargets" target="_none">Open Targets Team</a></li></a>
          </li>
