        <div id="depmap-omics-ccle" class="dataset">
          <h3><a href="/depmap-omics-ccle/">The Cancer Dependency Map (DepMap) Cancer Cell Line Encyclopedia (CCLE) Dataset</a></h3>
          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">bam</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">bioinformatics</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">biology</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">cancer</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">genetic</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">genomic</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">Homo sapiens</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">life sciences</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">short read sequencing</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">transcriptomics</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">whole exome sequencing</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">whole genome sequencing</span></p>
          <p>This dataset consists of whole genome sequencing (WGS), whole exome sequencing (WES), and RNA sequencing files generated from ~1000 cancer cell lines described in Ghandi et al., 2019.</p>
          <p><a href="/depmap-omics-ccle/">Details &rarr;</a></p>
