          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s41416-021-01359-0" class="" target="_none">Bridging the gap between cancer cell line models and tumours using gene expression data</a> by Noorbakhsh, Vazquez &amp; McFarland</li></a>
          </li>
