            <a href="https://www.dynsyslab.org/wp-content/papercite-data/pdf/burnett-ral21.pdf" class="" target="_none">Do we need to compensate for motion distortion and doppler effects in spinning radar navigation?</a> by K Burnett, A P Schoellig, T D Barfoot</li></a>
          </li>
