            <a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2105.14152.pdf" class="" target="_none">Radar odometry combining probabilistic estimation and unsupervised feature learning</a> by K Burnett, D J Yoon, A P Schoellig, T D Barfoot</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2203.10168" class="" target="_none">Boreas: A multi-season autonomous driving dataset</a> by K Burnett, D J Yoon, Y Wu, A Z Li, H Zhang, S Lu, J Qian, W Tseng, A Lambert, K YK Leung, A P Schoellig, Timothy D Barfoot</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2203.10174" class="" target="_none">Are We Ready for Radar to Replace Lidar in All-Weather Mapping and Localization?</a> by K Burnett, Y Wu, D J Yoon, A P Schoellig, T D Barfoot</li></a>
