          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://doi.org/10.1038/s41561-019-0510-8" class="" target="_none">Deep glacial troughs and stabilizing ridges unveiled beneath the margins of the Antarctic ice sheet</a> by Morlighem, M., Rignot, E., Binder, T. et al.</li></a>
