          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/32382149/" class="" target="_none">Environmental Determinants of cardiovasular disease: lessons learned from air pollution</a> by Al-Kindi SG, Brook RD, Biswal S, Rajagopalan S.</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.jci.org/articles/view/137315" class="" target="_none">Metabolic effects of air pollution exposure and reversibility</a> by Rajagopalan S, Park B, Palanivel R, et al.</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/32576878/" class="" target="_none">Comparison of differential accessibility analysis strategies for ATAC-seq data</a> by Gontarz P, Fu S, Xing X, Liu S, Miao B et.al.</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/32551139/" class="" target="_none">Epigenetic biomarkers and preterm birth</a> by Park B, Khanam R, Vinayachandran V, et.al.</li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
