            <a href="https://github.com/robintw/LatLongToWRS" class="" target="_none">LatLongToWRS</a> by <a href="https://blog.rtwilson.com/converting-latitudelongitude-co-ordinates-to-landsat-wrs-2-pathsrows/" target="_none">Robin Wilson</a></li></a>
          </li>
