          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://doi.org/10.1038/sdata.2015.22" class="" target="_none">Proteomic analysis of colon and rectal carcinoma using standard and customized databases
</a> by Slebos RJ, Wang X, Wang X, Zhang B, Tabb DL, Liebler DC</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://proteomics.cancer.gov/data-portal" class="" target="_none">CPTAC Data Portal</a> by <a href="https://proteomics.cancer.gov/" target="_none">National Cancer Institute</a></li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
