        <div id="hycom-gofs-3pt1-reanalysis" class="dataset">
          <h3><a href="/hycom-gofs-3pt1-reanalysis/">HYbrid Coordinate Ocean Model Global Ocean Forecast System Reanalysis</a></h3>
          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">global</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">oceans</span></p>
          <p>Global Ocean Forecasting System (GOFS) 3.1 output on the GLBv0.08 grid. The resolution is 0.08° resolution between 40°S and 40°N, 0.04° poleward of these latitudes. The temportal frequenct is 3 hourly. This data was created by the Naval Research Laboratory: Ocean Dynamics and Prediction Branch.</p>
