            <a href="https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.08.07.241729v2" class="" target="_none">Petabase-scale sequence alignment catalyses viral discovery</a> by Edgar R., Taylor J., Lin V., et al (2021)</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.07.28.224584v2" class="" target="_none">coronaSPAdes. From biosynthetic gene clusters to RNA viral assemblies</a> by Meleshko D., Hajirasouliha I., and Korobeynikov A. (2021)</li></a>
          </li>
