            <a href="https://doi.org/10.1038/s43247-023-00681-0" class="" target="_none">Uncertain future of sustainable fisheries environment in eastern boundary upwelling zones under climate change</a> by Chang et al. (2023)</li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
