            <a href="https://doi.org/10.1093/database/baac096" class="" target="_none">NEMAR: an open access data, tools, and compute resource operating on neuroelectromagnetic data</a> by A. Delorme, D. Truong, C. Youn, T. Mullen, A. Smetanin, S. Bhatt, S. Makeig</li></a>
          </li>
