          <p>High resolution, annual cropland and landcover maps for selected African countries developed by <a href="https://clarku.edu">Clark University</a>&#39;s <a href="https://agroimpacts.info/">Agricultural Impacts Research Group</a> using various machine learning approaches applied to Planet imagery, including field boundary and cultivated frequency maps, as well as multi-class land cover.</p>
