            <a href="https://computationalpathologygroup.github.io/ASAP/" class="" target="_none">ASAP Viewer</a> by <a href="https://www.diagnijmegen.nl/people/geert-litjens/" target="_none">Geert Litjens</a></li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/DIAGNijmegen/pathology-whole-slide-data" class="" target="_none">Whole slide data - python package for working with wholeslide images and annotations files</a> by <a href="https://www.diagnijmegen.nl/" target="_none">Diagnostic Image Analysis Group, Radboudumc, Nijmegen</a></li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://zenodo.org/records/13794656" class="" target="_none">Structured description of the MONKEY Challenge</a> by <a href="https://www.computationalpathologygroup.eu/" target="_none">Linda Studer, Dominique van Midden, Fazael Ayatollahi, Jeroen van der Laak</a></li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://monkey.grand-challenge.org/" class="" target="_none">MONKEY Challenge</a> by <a href="https://www.computationalpathologygroup.eu/" target="_none">Computational Pathology Group Radboudumc, Nijmegen</a></li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
