          <ul class="dataatwork-list">
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/blahner/mosaic-preprocessing/blob/main/src/fmriDatasetPreparation/create_hdf5/load_hdf5.ipynb" class="" target="_none">Load HDF5 file (Jupyter notebook)</a> by Benjamin Lahner</li></a>
          </li>
