          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/murtylab/mosaic-dataset/blob/master/examples/mosaic_synthetic_localizer.ipynb" class="" target="_none">Run a synthetic localizer experiment using MOSAIC&#x27;s brain-optimized models (Jupyter notebook)</a> by Benjamin Lahner</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://pypi.org/project/mosaic-dataset/" class="" target="_none">MOSAIC Python package (mosaic-dataset)</a> by Mayukh Deb</li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
