            <a href="https://github.com/stac-utils/pystac-client" class="" target="_none">PySTAC Client</a> by <a href="https://github.com/stac-utils/pystac-client/graphs/contributors" target="_none">PySTAC-Client Contributors</a></li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://stac.astrogeology.usgs.gov/docs/tutorials/basicpython/" class="" target="_none">Discovering and Downloading Data with Python</a> by <a href="https://astrogeology.usgs.gov" target="_none">J. Laura</a></li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://stac.astrogeology.usgs.gov/docs/examples/to_qgis/" class="" target="_none">Querying for Data in an ROI and Loading it into QGIS</a> by <a href="https://astrogeology.usgs.gov" target="_none">J. Laura</a></li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://stac.astrogeology.usgs.gov/docs/tutorials/cli/" class="" target="_none">Discovering and Downloading Data via the Command Line</a> by <a href="https://astrogeology.usgs.gov" target="_none">J. Laura</a></li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
