          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://doi.org/10.1109/TGRS.2016.2572724" class="" target="_none">A Robust Method to Generate a Consistent Time Series From DMSP/OLS Nighttime Light Data</a> by Qingling Zhang and Bhartendu Pandey and Keren C.Seto</li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
