            <a href="https://github.com/linklab-uva/rosbag2nuscenes" class="" target="_none">rosbag2nuscenes conversion library</a> by <a href="https://github.com/linklab-uva/rosbag2nuscenes" target="_none">John Chrosniak, Emory Ducote, John Link, Madhur Behl</a></li></a>
