        <div id="sparc" class="dataset">
          <h3><a href="/sparc/">SPARC: Datasets bridging the body and the brain</a></h3>
          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">bioinformatics</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">electrophysiology</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">life sciences</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">microscopy</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">neurophysiology</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">neuroscience</span></p>
          <p>The SPARC Datasets comprise a collection of scientific data that is focused
on bridging the body and the brain. The datasets focus on neural connectivity,
organ innervation and detailed anatomical mapping of the peripheral nervous system.
SPARC datasets distinguish themselves from other data resources through its multi-modal
approach to scientific data and integrates molecular, imaging, timeseries and other
datatypes associated with the interaction between the peripheral nervous system and 
organs. SPARC data provides a unique integrated effort to develop next generation mapping
of anatomical ...</p>
