        <div id="spartan-cloud" class="dataset">
          <h3><a href="/spartan-cloud/">SPARTAN Data</a></h3>
          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">air quality</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">environmental</span></p>
          <p>SPARTAN (Surface PARTiculate mAtter Network) measures and provides surface ambient particulate matter (PM2.5 and PM10) concentration and the chemical composition around the world, with the purpose of connecting ground-based PM2.5 and satellite remote sensing.</p>
