            <a href="https://doi.org/10.5194/amt-8-505-2015" class="" target="_none">SPARTAN: A global network to evaluate and enhance satellite-based estimates of ground-level particulate matter for global health applications</a> by Graydon Snider, et al.</li></a>
          </li>
