            <a href="https://spartan-cloud.readthedocs.io/en/latest/index.html" class="" target="_none">Tutorial on using SPARTAN data on AWS</a> by <a href="https://github.com/haihui-zhu" target="_none">Haihui Zhu</a></li></a>
          </li>
