            <a href="https://brainlife.io/docs/tutorial/aws-brainlife" class="" target="_none">Brainlife AWS Tutorials</a> by <a href="https://brainlife.io" target="_none">Brainlife</a></li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/brainlife/cli" class="" target="_none">Brainlife CLI (Command Line Interface)</a> by <a href="https://github.com/brainlife/cli" target="_none">Brainlife</a></li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://brainlife.io/pubs" class="" target="_none">Brainlife publications</a> by <a href="https://brainlife.io" target="_none">Brainlife</a></li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
