            <a href="http://github.com/gnss-ro/aws-opendata/tree/master/awsgnssroutils/" class="" target="_none">Utilities for Handling Data in the AWS Open Data Registry archive of GNSS Radio Occultation Data</a> by <a href="http://www.aer.com" target="_none">Stephen Leroy, Amy McVey</a></li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="http://github.com/gnss-ro/aws-opendata/tree/master/tutorials/" class="" target="_none">Tutorial Demonstrations for Working with GNSS Radio Occultation Data in AWS Open Data Registry archive</a> by Stephen Leroy, Amy McVey, Hailing Zhang, Chi Ao</li></a>
          </li>
