          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">genetic</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">genome wide association study</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">genomic</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">life sciences</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">population genetics</span></p>
          <p>A multi-ancestry analysis of 7,221 phenotypes using a generalized mixed model association testing framework, spanning 16,119 genome-wide association studies. We provide standard meta-analysis across all populations and with a leave-one-population-out approach for each trait. The data are provided in tsv format (per phenotype) and Hail MatrixTable (all phenotypes and variants). Metadata is provided in phenotype and variant manifests.</p>
          <p><a href="/broad-pan-ukb/">Details &rarr;</a></p>
