          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://pan.ukbb.broadinstitute.org/" class="" target="_none">Pan-ancestry genetic analysis of the UK Biobank</a> by Pan UKBB Team</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://hail.is" class="" target="_none">Hail</a> by <a href="https://hail.is/" target="_none">Hail Team</a></li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
