          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://osmcha.org" class="" target="_none">OSMCha</a> by <a href="https://github.com/willemarcel/" target="_none">Wille Marcel, Mapbox et al.</a></li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/real-changesets-parser" class="" target="_none">real-changesets-parser</a> by <a href="https://www.mapbox.com/" target="_none">Mapbox</a></li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.openstreetmap.org/user/geohacker/diary/40846" class="" target="_none">Preparing accurate history and caching changesets</a> by <a href="https://github.com/geohacker/" target="_none">Sajjad Anwar</a></li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
