        <div id="citrus-farm" class="dataset">
          <h3><a href="/citrus-farm/">CitrusFarm Dataset</a></h3>
          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">agriculture</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">computer vision</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">IMU</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">lidar</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">localization</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">mapping</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">robotics</span></p>
          <p>CitrusFarm is a multimodal agricultural robotics dataset that provides both multispectral images and navigational sensor data for localization, mapping and crop monitoring tasks. <ol>
<li>It was collected by a wheeled mobile robot in the Agricultural Experimental Station at the University of California Riverside in the summer of 2023. </li>
<li>It offers a total of nine sensing modalities, including stereo RGB, depth, monochrome, near-infrared and thermal images, as well as wheel odometry, LiDAR, IMU and GPS-RTK data. </li>
<li>It comprises seven sequences collected from three citrus tree fields, featuring various tree spe</li></ol>...</p>
