          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-031-47969-4_44" class="" target="_none">Multimodal Dataset for Localization, Mapping and Crop Monitoring in Citrus Tree Farms</a> by Hanzhe Teng, Yipeng Wang, Xiaoao Song and Konstantinos Karydis</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://ucr-robotics.github.io/Citrus-Farm-Dataset/download.html" class="" target="_none">Python script to download this dataset</a> by Hanzhe Teng et al.</li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
