            <a href="https://www.nrel.gov/docs/fy22osti/82837.pdf" class="" target="_none">The Geothermal Data Repository: Ten Years of Supporting the Geothermal Industry with Open Access to Geothermal Data</a> by J. Weers, A. Anderson, N. Taverna</li></a>
