          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id&#x3D;10.1371/journal.pone.0269425" class="" target="_none">Cohort profile: The Golden Retriever Lifetime Study (GRLS)</a> by Julia Labadie, Brenna Swafford, Mara DePena, Kathy Tietje, Rodney Page, Janet Patterson-Kane</li></a>
          </li>
