Please check your systems are prepared for these changes.<br><br>A numerical weather prediction forecast for the whole globe, with a resolution of approximately 0.09 degrees i.e. 10km (2,560 x 1,920 grid points). The data is available as NetCDF files. It&#39;s offered on a free, unsupported basis, so we don&#39;t recommend using it ...</p>
