<li>changes to existing parameters e.g. adding vertical levels and timesteps</li>
<li>the height_asl_on_pressure_levels parameter will be replaced by geopotential_height_on_pressure_levels<br><br></li>
</ul>
Please check your systems are prepared for these changes.<br><br>A high-resolution gridded weather forecast for the UK, with a resolution of 0.018 degrees, projected on to a 2km horizontal grid. The data is available as NetCDF files. It&#39;s offered on a free, unsupported basis, so we don’t recommend using it for any critical business purpos...</p>
