          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/OPERA-Cal-Val/OPERA_Applications/blob/main/RTC/notebooks/RTC_notebook.ipynb" class="" target="_none">Load, Mosaic, and Visualize OPERA RTC-S1 Data</a> by K. Venkataramani</li></a>
          </li>
