          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/link_gateway/2023AJ....165...71H/doi:10.3847/1538-3881/acaaa7" class="" target="_none">TESS-Gaia Light Curve, A PSF-based TESS FFI Light-curve Product</a> by Han, T. and Brandt, T.</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/spacetelescope/tike_content/blob/main/content/notebooks/tglc/tglc.ipynb" class="" target="_none">TGLC in the Cloud Jupyter Notebook</a> by MAST Staff</li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
