          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/nature23889" class="" target="_none">Strains, functions and dynamics in the expanded Human Microbiome Project</a> by Jason Lloyd-Price, Anup Mahurkar, Gholamali Rahnavard, Jonathan Crabtree, Joshua Orvis, A. Brantley Hall, et al.</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/nature06244" class="" target="_none">The Human Microbiome Project</a> by Peter J. Turnbaugh, Ruth E. Ley, Micah Hamady, Claire M. Fraser-Liggett, Rob Knight &amp; Jeffrey I. Gordon</li></a>
