          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/ScrollPrize/open-data/blob/main/examples/get-to-know-a-dataset.ipynb" class="" target="_none">Get To Know a Dataset: Vesuvius Challenge - CT Scans of Herculaneum Papyri</a> by <a href="https://scrollprize.org/" target="_none">Vesuvius Challenge Team</a></li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://scrollprize.org/tutorial" class="" target="_none">Vesuvius Challenge - Tutorials</a> by <a href="https://scrollprize.org/" target="_none">Vesuvius Challenge Team</a></li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
