          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">brain images</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">brain models</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">electron microscopy</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">electrophysiology</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">imaging</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">life sciences</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">Mus musculus</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">neurobiology</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">neuroimaging</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">neurophysiology</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">neuroscience</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">simulation neuroscience</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">single neuron models</span></p>
          <p>The Dendritic Consortium provides a multimodal dataset integrating calcium and voltage imaging, electrophysiology, electron microscopy, proteomics, and computational models of Baz1a pyramidal neurons in the mouse primary visual cortex (V1).</p>
