            <a href="https://doi.org/10.1175/JAMC-D-15-0153.1" class="" target="_none">Dynamical Downscaling of ERA-Interim Temperature and Precipitation for Alaska</a> by Peter A. Bieniek, Uma S. Bhatt, John E. Walsh, T. Scott Rupp, Jing Zhang, Jeremy R. Krieger, and Rick Lader</li></a>
