          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/dynamical-org/notebooks/blob/main/ecmwf-aifs-single-forecast.ipynb" class="" target="_none">ECMWF AIFS Single forecast — Quickstart</a> by <a href="https://dynamical.org" target="_none">dynamical.org</a></li></a>
