        <div id="mast-jwst" class="dataset">
          <h3><a href="/mast-jwst/">James Webb Space Telescope (JWST)</a></h3>
          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">astronomy</span></p>
          <p>The James Webb Space Telescope (JWST) is the world&#39;s next flagship infrared observatory led by NASA with its partners, ESA (European Space Agency), and CSA (Canadian Space Agency). JWST offers scientists the opportunity to observe galaxy evolution, the formation of stars and planets, exoplanetary systems, and our own solar system, in ways never before possible.</p>
          <p><a href="/mast-jwst/">Details &rarr;</a></p>
          <h4>Usage examples</h4>
