            <a href="https://journals.ametsoc.org/view/journals/clim/27/6/jcli-d-12-00823.1.xml" class="" target="_none">The NCEP Climate Forecast System Version 2</a> by Saha, Suranjana, and Coauthors</li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
