          <p><p>The Global Ensemble Forecast System (GEFS) is a National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA) National Centers for Environmental Prediction (NCEP) weather forecast model. GEFS creates 31 separate forecasts (ensemble members) to describe the range of forecast uncertainty.</p>
