          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://doi.org/10.3390/atmos14071110" class="" target="_none">NOAA’s Global Forecast System Data in the Cloud for Community Air Quality Modeling. Atmosphere 2023, 14, 1110.</a> by Campbell, P.C.; Jiang, W.; Moon, Z.; Zinn, S.; Tang, Y.</li></a>
