            <a href="https://www.nanoos.org/products/j-scope/about_the_model.php" class="" target="_none">J-SCOPE About the Model</a> by <a href="https://www.nanoos.org/products/j-scope/home.php" target="_none">NOAA J_SCOPE</a></li></a>
          </li>
