          <h4>Usage examples</h4>
          <ul class="dataatwork-list">
          <li>
            <a href="https://doi.org/10.1175/WAF-D-22-0162.1" class="" target="_none">The impact of tropical SST biases on the S2S precipitation forecast skill over the Contiguous United States in the UFS global coupled model</a> by Hedanqiu Bai, Bin Li, Avichal Mehra, Jessica Meixner, Shrinivas Moorthi, Sulagna Ray, Lydia Stefanova, Jiande Wang, Jun Wang, Denise Worthen, Fanglin Yang, and Cristiana Stan</li></a>
          </li>
