            <a href="https://agupubs.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/pdf/10.1029/2022GL102392" class="" target="_none">Advances in Seasonal Predictions of Arctic Sea Ice With NOAA UFS</a> by Jieshun Zhu, Wanqiu Wang, Yanyun Liu, Arun Kumar, and David DeWitt</li></a>
          </li>
