          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/OPERA-Cal-Val/OPERA_Applications/blob/main/CSLC/Volcano/Map_Deformation_LavaFlow_using_CSLC-S1.ipynb" class="" target="_none">Generate interferograms and map the lava flow emplacement using OPERA CSLC-S1</a> by M. Grace Bato</li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
