            <a href="https://open-cravat.readthedocs.io/en/latest/AWS-OpenData.html" class="" target="_none">Changing the OpenCRAVAT store url</a> by Kyle Moad</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://opencravat.org" class="" target="_none">OpenCRAVAT</a> by <a href="https://karchinlab.org" target="_none">Karchinlab</a></li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p><a href="/open-cravat/#usageexamples">See 2 usage examples &rarr;</a></p>
        </div>
        <div id="ohsu-cnl" class="dataset">
          <h3><a href="/ohsu-cnl/">Oregon Health &amp; Science University Chronic Neutrophilic Leukemia Dataset</a></h3>
          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">cancer</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">genomic</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">life sciences</span></p>
          <p>The OHSU-CNL study offers the whole exome and RNA-sequencing on a cohort of 100 cases with rare
hematologic malignancies such as Chronic neutrophilic leukemia (CNL), atypical chronic myeloid
leukemia (aCML), and unclassified myelodysplastic syndrome/myeloproliferative neoplasms
(MDS/MPN-U). This dataset contains open RNA-Seq Gene Expression Quantification data.</p>
          <p><a href="/ohsu-cnl/">Details &rarr;</a></p>
          <h4>Usage examples</h4>
