            <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2406.06776" class="" target="_none">SeeFar: Satellite Agnostic Multi-Resolution Dataset for Geospatial Foundation Models</a> by Lowman, J., Zheng, K. L., Fraser, R., The, J. V. G., &amp; Valipour, M.</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://coastalcarbon.ai/seefar" class="" target="_none">Getting Started with SeeFar for Multi-Resolution Geospatial Analysis</a> by <a href="https://www.coastalcarbon.ai/team" target="_none">James Lowman - Coastal Carbon</a></li></a>
          </li>
