        <div id="colorado-elevation-data" class="dataset">
          <h3><a href="/colorado-elevation-data/">State of Colorado Elevation Data</a></h3>
          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">geospatial</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">imaging</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">mapping</span></p>
          <p>The State of Colorado has gathered public historical elevation data.</p>
          <p><a href="/colorado-elevation-data/">Details &rarr;</a></p>
          <h4>Usage examples</h4>
          <ul class="dataatwork-list">
