            <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/industries/exploring-the-uniprot-protein-knowledgebase-with-aws-open-data-and-amazon-neptune/" class="aws-link" target="_none">Exploring the UniProt protein knowledgebase with AWS Open Data and Amazon Neptune</a> by Eric Greene, Rafa Xu, Yuan Shi (AWS)</li></a>
