        <div id="eot-web-archive" class="dataset">
          <h3><a href="/eot-web-archive/">End of Term Web Archive Dataset</a></h3>
          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">archives</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">internet</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">natural language processing</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">web archive</span></p>
          <p>The End of Term Web Archive (EOT) captures and saves U.S. Government websites at the end of presidential administrations.  The EOT has thus far preserved websites from administration changes in 2008, 2012, 2016, 2020  and 2024.  Data from these web crawls have been made openly available in several formats in this dataset.</p>
