          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">carbon</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">climate</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">csv</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">electricity</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">energy</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">energy modeling</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">environmental</span></p>
          <p>The Climate TRACE coalition has developed and maintains free global hourly Build Margin data, also known as MBERs, that are compliant with the Greenhouse Gas Protocol&#39;s Project Protocol electricity sector guidance, Guidelines for Grid-Connected Electricity Projects (&quot;GHGP Guidelines&quot;).</p>
