          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.amazon.science/publications/gazetteer-enhanced-named-entity-recognition-for-code-mixed-web-queries" class="" target="_none">Gazetteer Enhanced Named Entity Recognition for Code-Mixed Web Queries</a> by Besnik Fetahu, Anjie Fang, Oleg Rokhlenko and Shervin Malmasi</li></a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://assets.amazon.science/95/4c/47c2afd44236ac1a05d184e7813e/dynamic-gazetteer-integration-in-multilingual-models-for-cross-lingual-and-cross-domain-named-entity-recognition.pdf" class="" target="_none">Dynamic Gazetteer Integration in Multilingual Models for Cross-Lingual and Cross-Domain Named Entity Recognition</a> by Besnik Fetahu, Anjie Fang, Oleg Rokhlenko and Shervin Malmasi</li></a>
          </li>
