            <a href="https://aclanthology.org/2022.coling-1.334.pdf" class="" target="_none">MultiCoNER: A Large-scale Multilingual Dataset for Complex Named Entity Recognition</a> by Shervin Malmasi, Anjie Fang, Besnik Fetahu, Sudipta Kar, Oleg Rokhlenko</li></a>
          </li>
