          <ul class="dataatwork-list">
          <li>
            <a href="https://portal.opentopography.org/datasets" class="" target="_none">OpenTopography access and processing of NOAA Coastal Lidar Data</a> by <a href="https://opentopography.org/" target="_none">OpenTopography</a></li></a>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p><a href="/noaa-coastal-lidar/#usageexamples">See 1 usage example &rarr;</a></p>
