          <ul class="dataatwork-list">
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/aws-samples/aws-smsl-predict-airquality-via-weather/" class="aws-link" target="_none">ML Demo: Predicting Air Quality w/ ASDI NOAA + OpenAQ Datasets in SageMaker Studio Lab (SMSL)</a> by Aaron Soto</li></a>
