          <p>This BIDS-formatted dataset provides multimodal brain MRI data from 150 patients with primary central nervous system lymphoma (PCNSL), including T1-weighted, contrast-enhanced T1-weighted, FLAIR, and ADC sequences. The dataset includes expert-annotated lesion segmentations with radiomic features, along with anonymized clinical data including demographics, diagnosis history, and medications.</p>
