          <h3><a href="/nasa-avuelo/">NASA AVUELO Project</a></h3>
          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">atmosphere</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">netcdf</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">oceans</span></p>
          <p>An inventory of NASA&#39;s airborne and field campaigns for Earth Science...</p>
          <p><a href="/nasa-avuelo/">Details &rarr;</a></p>
