          <p><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">elevation</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">land cover</span><span class="label label-info tag link-tag">satellite imagery</span></p>
          <p>This dataset contains vegetation canopy metrics for the Greater Kruger National Park region of South Africa for 2007-2010 and 2015-2024. Metrics include relative height 98th percentile (RH98), fractional canopy cover, and foliage height diversity. This dataset contains vegetation canopy metrics for the Greater Kruger National Park region of South Africa. Metrics include relative height 98th percentile (RH98), fractional canopy cover, and foliage height diversity. They were derived by modeling a sample of Global Ecosystem Dynamics Investigation (GEDI) Level 2A Elevation and Height Metrics and L...</p>
          <p><a href="/nasa-biodiversity/">Details &rarr;</a></p>
        </div>
