          <p>PersonPath22 is a large-scale multi-person tracking dataset containing 236 videos captured mostly from static-mounted cameras,  collected from sources where we were given the rights to redistribute the content and participants have given explicit consent. Each video has ground-truth annotations including both bounding boxes and tracklet-ids for all the persons in each frame.</p>
