          <p>This dataset is part of the paper &quot;McPhraSy: Multi-Context Phrase Similarity and Clustering&quot; by DN Cohen et al (2022). The purpose of PCD is to evaluate the quality of semantic-based clustering of noun phrases. The phrases were collected from the [Amazon Review Dataset] (<a href="https://nijianmo.github.io/amazon/">https://nijianmo.github.io/amazon/</a>).</p>
